```
package main

import (
    "fmt"
    "math"
)

func main() {
    res := math.Log(4)
    fmt.Println(res)

    res = math.Log(10.2)
    fmt.Println(res)

    res = math.Log(-10)
    fmt.Println(res)
}
```
